<p>The <span class="title-main">African American &amp; African Studies </span>is an interdisciplinary field of study in the humanities, arts, and social sciences. Students investigate the history and culture of communities of African descent in the United States, on the African continent, and in diasporic communities of Canada, South America, the Caribbean, Europe, and Asia.</p>
